      "raw_text": "The apathy shown prior to the\nelection seems to have disappear\ned and confidence in local securi-\nties seems to be returned. The\nmovement in Panhandle is very\ndisconcerting. and this is probably\ndue to the fact that there are deals\nand counterdeals under way that\nwill materially affect the future of\nthe company. 1t is understood that\nthe Bunker Hill & Sullivan has\nacquired foothold through agents\nwho are busy picking up outside\nstock and taking options on some."
